                <tr>
                  <td class="tit_icon">MANAGING COMMITTEE</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><span class="text">The Managing Committee shall consist of not more than 15  Member declared elected /select and such elected/select members shall amongst  themselves elect/select the following Office-Bearers in its First Managing  Committee Meeting , after such election/selection.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="2%"><img src="images/bull.jpg" width="6" height="6" /></td>
                        <td width="98%" align="left" class="text"><strong>Chairman</strong></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td><img src="images/bull.jpg" width="6" height="6" /></td>
